<A HREF="http://www.fohguild.org/images/WoW5.jpg"><img src=http://www.fohguild.org/images/wow5_sm.jpg border=0></A> <br />
<br />
Oh damn, I almost forgot. The bank in the human city HAD A VELVET FREAKIN ROPE LINE! VELVET I TELL YOU! Where do I sign up?</font>
			
			<br>
            <br>
